title: Lunchbox Fights For Justice In Court + Bobby Almost Hits A Bicyclist
itunes:title: Lunchbox Fights For Justice In Court + Bobby Almost Hits A Bicyclist
description:
Lunchbox recaps his experience in court fighting a $10 parking ticket that he believes was unfair. Bobby tells story about almost hitting a bicyclist while driving in Austin yesterday. Also, Bobby gives the guys awards for their best body parts.
